title: Google\Cloud\AutoMl\V1\ImageObjectDetectionEvaluationMetrics
name: ImageObjectDetectionEvaluationMetrics
description:
Model evaluation metrics for image object detection problems.

Evaluates prediction quality of labeled bounding boxes.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.automl.v1.ImageObjectDetectionEvaluationMetrics

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.evaluated_bounding_box_count
params.description: Output only. The total number of bounding boxes (i.e. summed over all images) the ground truth used to create this evaluation had.

params.name: data.bounding_box_metrics_entries
params.description: Output only. The bounding boxes match metrics for each Intersection-over-union threshold 0.05,0.10,...,0.95,0.96,0.97,0.98,0.99 and each label confidence threshold 0.05,0.10,...,0.95,0.96,0.97,0.98,0.99 pair.

params.name: data.bounding_box_mean_average_precision
params.description: Output only. The single metric for bounding boxes evaluation: the mean_average_precision averaged over all bounding_box_metrics_entries.
